name: Ryne (Final fantasy XIV) - LoRA
description:
Ryen Is a lovely character from Final Fantasy XIV patch 5.0, I used Never Ending Dream (NED) as a base for training to basically turn a game character Ryen into a real one. I used a lot of screenshots of the game for training. The overall style of the model is consistent with the game, and it works well on 2.5D checkpoint.

Recommended weight 0.6~0.8 Checkpoint: majicMIX realistic

Tag: Ryen, white dress, bangs, orange hair,
